    {
        "content": "<p>Here's what I get from one attempt at using <code>wlog</code>:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kd\">example</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">Œ±</span> <span class=\"n\">Œ≤</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"kt\">Type</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">f</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">set</span> <span class=\"n\">Œ±</span> <span class=\"bp\">‚Üí</span> <span class=\"n\">Œ≤</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">injective</span> <span class=\"n\">f</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span>\n<span class=\"kd\">begin</span>\n  <span class=\"k\">assume</span> <span class=\"n\">S</span> <span class=\"n\">T</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">hST</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">f</span> <span class=\"n\">S</span> <span class=\"bp\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">f</span> <span class=\"n\">T</span><span class=\"o\">),</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">apply</span> <span class=\"n\">le_antisymm</span><span class=\"o\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">wlog</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">T</span> <span class=\"bp\">‚â§</span> <span class=\"n\">S</span> <span class=\"n\">using</span> <span class=\"n\">S</span> <span class=\"n\">T</span><span class=\"o\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"c\">/-</span><span class=\"cm\"></span>\n<span class=\"cm\">  3 goals</span>\n<span class=\"cm\">  case cases</span>\n<span class=\"cm\">  Œ± Œ≤ : Type,</span>\n<span class=\"cm\">  f : set Œ± ‚Üí Œ≤,</span>\n<span class=\"cm\">  S T : set Œ±,</span>\n<span class=\"cm\">  hST : f S = f T</span>\n<span class=\"cm\">  ‚ä¢ T ‚â§ S ‚à® S ‚â§ T</span>\n\n<span class=\"cm\">  case main</span>\n<span class=\"cm\">  Œ± Œ≤ : Type,</span>\n<span class=\"cm\">  f : set Œ± ‚Üí Œ≤,</span>\n<span class=\"cm\">  S T : set Œ±,</span>\n<span class=\"cm\">  case : T ‚â§ S,</span>\n<span class=\"cm\">  hST : f S = f T</span>\n<span class=\"cm\">  ‚ä¢ S ‚â§ T</span>\n\n<span class=\"cm\">  Œ± Œ≤ : Type,</span>\n<span class=\"cm\">  f : set Œ± ‚Üí Œ≤,</span>\n<span class=\"cm\">  S T : set Œ±,</span>\n<span class=\"cm\">  hST : f S = f T</span>\n<span class=\"cm\">  ‚ä¢ T ‚â§ S</span>\n<span class=\"cm\">  -/</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
