        "timestamp": 1618381880
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>FWIW I would set up your proof like this:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kd\">lemma</span> <span class=\"n\">mk_opens_R_aux</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"bp\">#</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">opens</span> <span class=\"n\">‚Ñù</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"bp\">‚â§</span> <span class=\"bp\">#</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">set</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">‚Ñö</span> <span class=\"bp\">√ó</span> <span class=\"n\">‚Ñö</span><span class=\"o\">))</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span>\n<span class=\"kd\">begin</span>\n  <span class=\"c1\">-- An open set in ‚Ñù is uniquely determined by the rational balls included in it.</span>\n  <span class=\"c1\">-- (Any dense set would do just as well in place of ‚Ñö.)</span>\n  <span class=\"k\">let</span> <span class=\"n\">f</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span> <span class=\"bp\">Œª</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">S</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">opens</span> <span class=\"n\">‚Ñù</span><span class=\"o\">),</span> <span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">p</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">‚Ñö</span> <span class=\"bp\">√ó</span> <span class=\"n\">‚Ñö</span> <span class=\"bp\">|</span> <span class=\"n\">ball</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">p.1</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">‚Ñù</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"n\">p.2</span> <span class=\"bp\">‚äÜ</span> <span class=\"n\">S</span><span class=\"o\">},</span>\n  <span class=\"k\">suffices</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"bp\">‚àÄ</span> <span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">S</span> <span class=\"n\">T</span><span class=\"o\">},</span> <span class=\"n\">f</span> <span class=\"n\">S</span> <span class=\"bp\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">f</span> <span class=\"n\">T</span> <span class=\"bp\">‚Üí</span> <span class=\"n\">S</span> <span class=\"bp\">‚â§</span> <span class=\"n\">T</span><span class=\"o\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"o\">{</span> <span class=\"n\">exact</span> <span class=\"bp\">@</span><span class=\"n\">mk_le_of_injective</span> <span class=\"n\">_</span> <span class=\"n\">_</span> <span class=\"n\">f</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">Œª</span> <span class=\"n\">S</span> <span class=\"n\">T</span> <span class=\"n\">hST</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">this</span> <span class=\"n\">hST</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">antisymm</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">this</span> <span class=\"n\">hST.symm</span><span class=\"o\">))</span> <span class=\"o\">},</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">intros</span> <span class=\"n\">S</span> <span class=\"n\">T</span> <span class=\"n\">hST</span> <span class=\"n\">x</span> <span class=\"n\">hxS</span><span class=\"o\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"k\">have</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"bp\">‚Üë</span><span class=\"n\">S</span> <span class=\"bp\">‚àà</span> <span class=\"bp\">ùìù</span> <span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"k\">from</span> <span class=\"n\">mem_nhds_sets</span> <span class=\"n\">S.property</span> <span class=\"n\">hxS</span><span class=\"o\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"bp\">...</span> <span class=\"c1\">-- as before</span>\n<span class=\"kd\">end</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
